transcript:

Executive: Unka to number add kar diye the mam kal.
Customer: Sir secondary number ye 046 wala?
Executive: Haan usi number pe wo kar diye the change kiye the unka number dale the.
Customer: Actually ye change hua nahi hai to theek hai main connect kar le rahi hu.
Executive: Theek hai.
Customer: Theek hai sir.
